114
00:10:30,863 --> 00:10:33,599
She doesn't know
what insomnia is, Jack.

115
00:10:33,699 --> 00:10:34,800
It's nothing, honey.

116
00:10:34,900 --> 00:10:37,103
Just a bunch of
sleepless nights.

117
00:10:37,203 --> 00:10:38,270
So?

118
00:10:38,371 --> 00:10:41,040
A person can't be expected
to know everything.

119
00:10:44,076 --> 00:10:46,779
Do you know where Illyria is?

120
