122
00:10:54,453 --> 00:10:59,091
Shakespeare's "Twelfth
Night" was in Illyria.

123
00:11:01,961 --> 00:11:05,464
I was in a production
once of "Twelfth Night."

124
00:11:05,564 --> 00:11:08,167
You were in "Twelfth Night?"

125
00:11:08,267 --> 00:11:09,068
