144
00:11:57,583 --> 00:11:58,417
Dapper.

145
00:11:58,517 --> 00:12:00,186
Distinguished.

146
00:12:00,286 --> 00:12:01,654
Rich.

147
00:12:01,754 --> 00:12:03,022
Good looking.

148
00:12:03,122 --> 00:12:07,293
