176
00:13:04,216 --> 00:13:06,085
We're shooting "Conquest."

177
00:13:08,654 --> 00:13:12,491
[laughing]

178
00:13:12,591 --> 00:13:17,163
Everybody is trying to get
a glimpse of Charles Boyer

179
00:13:17,263 --> 00:13:18,831
as Napoleon.

180
00:13:18,931 --> 00:13:20,366
And Miss Garbo?

181
00:13:20,466 --> 00:13:23,903
Contrary to popular
opinion, Miss Garbo

182
00:13:24,003 --> 00:13:25,504
can be really quite affable.

183
00:13:28,140 --> 00:13:34,413
Sometimes, after hours, off
the set, Miss Gustafsson--

184
00:13:34,513 --> 00:13:36,148
that's her real name--

185
00:13:36,248 --> 00:13:41,854
and I sit around in our
underwear, chewing the fat.

186
00:13:41,954 --> 00:13:45,224
Greta cooks up a batch
of Swedish meatballs.

187
00:13:45,324 --> 00:13:51,897
Jack, Miss Garbo and I have
a very healthy relationship.

188
00:13:51,997 --> 00:13:54,300
I have a healthy
relationship with the woman

189
