I work for, unlike some
people I could mention.

190
00:14:00,105 --> 00:14:04,977
I'm going to pretend
you didn't say that.

191
00:14:05,077 --> 00:14:10,082
You pretend anything you want.

192
00:14:10,182 --> 00:14:15,521
Greta, Miss Garbo with
the bashful Valkyrie.

193
00:14:15,621 --> 00:14:18,257
Mm-hm.

194
00:14:18,357 --> 00:14:20,759
Here, Shirley.

195
00:14:20,859 --> 00:14:22,294
You owe it to yourself.

196
00:14:22,394 --> 00:14:23,195
Jack.

197
00:14:28,167 --> 00:14:31,070
I have such an enormous
debt to myself,

198
00:14:31,170 --> 00:14:34,073
it would take more than a
lifetime to pay it back.

199
00:14:34,173 --> 00:14:36,275
Whiskey can do magic
for lonely people, Shirl.

200
00:14:41,747 --> 00:14:44,283
Whiskey.

201
00:14:44,383 --> 00:14:45,217
Morphine.

202
