205
00:14:56,328 --> 00:14:57,129
Hi.

206
00:15:05,604 --> 00:15:06,906
I'm a stand-in.

207
00:15:07,006 --> 00:15:07,940
I'm OK.

208
00:15:08,040 --> 00:15:10,376
