Stand-ins Never Die.

246
00:16:26,552 --> 00:16:29,855
Course, she calls it
Fuck this Occupation.

247
00:16:29,955 --> 00:16:31,256
We never could agree.

248
00:16:31,357 --> 00:16:33,492
I brought some comestibles.

249
00:16:33,592 --> 00:16:35,994
Comestibles?

250
00:16:36,095 --> 00:16:37,529
A lot of them.

251
00:16:37,629 --> 00:16:39,798
MONICA: I know what combustibles
are, but what are they?

252
00:16:39,898 --> 00:16:40,899
Food, babe.
Eats.

253
00:16:40,999 --> 00:16:41,834
Vittles.

254
00:16:41,934 --> 00:16:42,968
MONICA: Oh.

255
00:16:43,068 --> 00:16:45,070
Miss Unaware,
that's you, honey.

256
00:16:45,170 --> 00:16:47,639
MONICA: I'm not so unaware.

257
00:16:47,740 --> 00:16:48,907
Aware, even.

258
00:16:49,007 --> 00:16:50,542
Will you look at
these comestibles?

259
00:16:50,642 --> 00:16:51,777
God!

260
00:16:51,877 --> 00:16:54,680
It's [inaudible] Do you
think I'd show up to my best

261
00:16:54,780 --> 00:16:56,749
friend's party empty-handed?

262
00:16:56,849 --> 00:16:58,016
I don't think so.

263
00:16:58,117 --> 00:16:59,752
I'd better put this
all in the kitchen.

264
00:16:59,852 --> 00:17:01,754
OK, well I'll help.

265
00:17:01,854 --> 00:17:02,755
OK, come on.

266
00:17:19,004 --> 00:17:24,042
If you're so smart,
what's a Valkyrie?

267
00:17:24,143 --> 00:17:28,580
Garbo's bashful Valkyrie.

268
00:17:28,680 --> 00:17:30,115
So what is a Valkyrie?

269
00:17:33,452 --> 00:17:38,090
SHIRLEY: In Norse mythology,
she's the maiden of Odin.

270
00:17:38,190 --> 00:17:43,262
She conducts the souls of
dead heroes to Valhalla.

271
00:17:43,362 --> 00:17:47,566
That's the Viking version
of heaven, to you.

